### Upload de imagem para Ponto de Interesse
#### Substitua "1" pelo ID do ponto de interesse criado

POST http://localhost:8787/attachments?type=cover&pointOfInterestId=1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary123

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="point-cover.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./tests/images/sample.jpg
--boundary123--

### Upload de imagem para galeria do Ponto de Interesse

POST http://localhost:8787/attachments?type=galery&pointOfInterestId=1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary123

--boundary123
